  <entry>
    <title>SnailGitLite或SnailSVN无法将difftool.sh安装到脚本目录</title>
    <link href="http://blog.asroads.com/post/b02e85.html"/>
    <id>http://blog.asroads.com/post/b02e85.html</id>
    <published>2021-05-08T10:19:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-05-08T10:27:58.353Z</updated>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;Mac系统中SVN能和&lt;a href=&quot;https://tortoisesvn.net/downloads.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;TortoiseSVN&lt;/a&gt;（Windows环境）版本控制软件媲美的软件不多，很多都是收费的，Git有&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.sourcetreeapp.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Sourcetree&lt;/a&gt;免费可以用来代替，&lt;a href=&quot;https://langui.net/snailgit/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;SnailGitLite&lt;/a&gt;或&lt;a href=&quot;https://langui.net/snailsvn/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;SnailSVN&lt;/a&gt; 这两款软件操作起来很像TortoiseSVN特别是文件可以有红绿蓝三色标识 更改 无变动 添加的状态，这里说说Mac上用这俩软件遇到的问题：无法将 &lt;strong&gt;difftool.sh&lt;/strong&gt; 安装到脚本目录！未能拷贝“difftool.sh”，因为您没有访问“net.langui.SnailSVN.DiffTool”的权限。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
